# Contributing

Development Setup

1. Install Packages

```
pnpm install
```

2. Start hot reload Development Server

```
pnpm dev
```

3. Output a release file

```
pnpm build
```

## Support

For support contact me. The fastest way to reach me is on discord @1upfunniguy. You can also use my email, sad.spongebob.dev@gmail.com
